LindseyGraham.com

Today was a big day for me. It's good to be home.

Friend - I wanted to share a photo of a very proud moment for
me. Earlier today I officially put my name on the ballot for
president in my home state of South Carolina.

This was a big day for me, and I was honored to have my family
and friends by my side. It's good to be home.

Thank you, as always, for your support. I hope I will see you
soon on the campaign trail.

Lindsey

